{"data":[{"date":"07:04 10/07","title":"Luis Enrique l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michel Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique sau khi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 La Roja kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Enrique ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0110T TBN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLuis Enrique thay th\u1ebf Fernando Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1m ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, RFEF \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui do nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Luis-Enrique-len-DT-TBN.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salgado \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Enrique</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Michel Salgado c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Luis Enrique c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u201d, Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a FIFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEnrique \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Barcelona v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0103n 3, l\u00e0 HLV t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng Hierro trong 2 ng\u00e0y, Enrique c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1094","checkdouble":"190812"},{"date":"07:25 10/07","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Real Madrid b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho M.U v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/sao-tre-real-madrid-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-va-cac-dai-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ec9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi Edwin van der Sar \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nB\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNgay t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Sau khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Euro 2016, C\u0110V B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng trong n\u0103m 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Edwin-Van-der-Sar-du-doan-Bi-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. T\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (11/7). H\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg</span><br />\r\n<span>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van der Sar tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Man United, Edwin van der Sar c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o B\u1ec9. Anh c\u00e0ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" title=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/thu-mon-Van-Der-Sar.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3\u201d, Van der Sar n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Omnisport. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 Lan, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Anderlecht l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Champions League b\u1ecb th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ph\u00e1p, Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u00dd, \u0110\u1ee9c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup, nh\u01b0 Croatia. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1093","checkdouble":"190813"},{"date":"07:44 10/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7: 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-107-48-gio-nua-ronaldo-se-la-nguoi-cua-juve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea t\u00ednh \"h\u1edbt tay tr\u00ean\" m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Man City. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Tuttosport, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n Maurizio Sarri, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge thay Antonio Conte. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Chelsea tin \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo Sky Sports, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Cristiano Ronaldo sang Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Jorge Mendes v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid, Florentino Perez s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern. </strong>Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Pini Zahavi c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Ba Lan, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho Lewy c\u0169ng v\u01a1i b\u1edbt. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern ph\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u00e2n binh Juventus m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Ronaldo n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. </strong>Emre Can m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. Juve m\u1edbi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. </strong>Raheem Sterling \u0111ang nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Eric Dier v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao Man City nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh. Anh tin c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Sterling l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling\" title=\"Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bo-doi-huyen-thoai-mu-bao-ve-sao-man-city-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u1ee3i khen c\u00e1ch Sterling \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xavi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui. </strong>Vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xavi, anh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</strong> Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1092","checkdouble":"190814"},{"date":"07:53 10/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1ea1i St. Petersburg.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng danh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng N'Golo Kante, Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0 Paul Pogba gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. \u1ede hai c\u00e1nh, Les Bleus c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Antoine Griezmann v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n Benjamin Pavard v\u00e0 Lucas Hernandez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng trong c\u00e1ch tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n g\u1ed1c Phi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 117) b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 117) b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 1h ng\u00e0y 11/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u00f2n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0i nghi th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong c\u1ee7a Olivier Giroud. C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec t\u1edbi nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t. Giroud v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6/9 b\u00e0n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Giroud l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann vs Mbappe cua Phap\" title=\"Griezmann vs Mbappe cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Griezmann-vs-Mbappe-cua-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ec9 b\u1ee9t l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. C\u0169ng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Khi chuy\u1ec3n sang 4-3-3 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Kevin De Bruyne hay Axel Witsel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd chuy\u1ec3n sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. \u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 socola c\u00f3 Romelu Lukaku kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" title=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Thomas-Vermaelen-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Bi-vs-Phap-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Lukaku s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, Eden Hazard khi th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, khi th\u00ec ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u201cs\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o\u201d. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Lukaku l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Hazard 2 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi 1 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Meunier\" title=\"hau ve Meunier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/hau-ve-Meunier.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi thi\u1ebfu Meunier l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9. Cho t\u1edbi nay, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 5 b\u00e0n thua v\u1edbi 2 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Tunisia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd b\u1ecb k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 1 b\u00e0n thua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Martinez.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>N\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng. Gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t kho\u00e9t c\u00e1nh s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante va Messi\" title=\"Kante va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea,-khac-tinh-cua-Messi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n B\u1ec9. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. C\u00f2n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i, nh\u1eefng Nacer Chadli hay Yannick Carrasco \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 sau v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Griezmann hay Mbappe? R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n! Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. Song d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 14.Matuidi, 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 9.Giroud, 7.Griezmann.<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ec9 (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Courtois - 22.Chadli, 2.Alderweireld, 4.Kompany, 5.Vertonghen - 8.Fellaini, 6.Witsel, 19.Dembele - 9.Lukaku, 7.De Bruyne, 10.Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 3-2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Phap vs Bi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Phap-vs-Bi-(4-3-3-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1091","checkdouble":"190815"},{"date":"08:13 10/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/van-der-sar-du-doan-bi-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ec9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi Edwin van der Sar \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nB\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNgay t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Sau khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Euro 2016, C\u0110V B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng trong n\u0103m 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Edwin-Van-der-Sar-du-doan-Bi-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. T\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (11/7). H\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg</span><br />\r\n<span>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van der Sar tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Man United, Edwin van der Sar c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o B\u1ec9. Anh c\u00e0ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" title=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/thu-mon-Van-Der-Sar.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3\u201d, Van der Sar n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Omnisport. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 Lan, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Anderlecht l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Champions League b\u1ecb th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ph\u00e1p, Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u00dd, \u0110\u1ee9c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup, nh\u01b0 Croatia. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1090","checkdouble":"190816"},{"date":"08:46 10/07","title":"\"Mbappe l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a R\u00f4 b\u00e9o, Henry v\u00e0 Cristiano\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Daniel van Buyten ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo Brazil, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Thierry Henry.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van Buyten \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mbappe</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf c\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG. Ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a PSG, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Neymar v\u00e0 Cavani h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daniel van Buyten ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Daniel van Buyten ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Daniel-van-Buyten-phat-bieu-ve-Kylian-Mbappe-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van Buyten \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao\u00a0</span>Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Mbappe c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaniel van Buyten ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo Brazil, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Thierry Henry.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u00ecn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo Brazil, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a R\u00f4 b\u00e9o.\u00a0 Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t Ronaldo n\u1eefa trong ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMbappe c\u0169ng mang d\u00e1ng d\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Henry, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 22 ho\u1eb7c 23, Mbappe s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Van Buyten tin B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p 2-1</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 vs Ph\u00e1p</span> trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Anh ho\u1eb7c Croatia trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Van Buyten kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Phap vs Bi\" title=\"Preview Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van Buyten tin B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p 2-1</span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 50-50. B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1089","checkdouble":"190820"},{"date":"08:46 10/07","title":"\u0110T Croatia m\u1ea5t HLV v\u00ec khi\u00eau kh\u00edch ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Ognjen Vukojevic m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 do ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110T Croatia m\u1ea5t HLV v\u00ec khi\u00eau kh\u00edch ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dalic va BHL Croatia\" title=\"Dalic va BHL Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia v\u1eeba sa th\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec khi\u00eau kh\u00edch n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia&nbsp;m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Ognjen Vukojevic kh\u1ecfi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0y. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng Ognjen Vukojevic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadm m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, HLV Vukojevjc v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi h\u00e9t l\u1edbn c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ukraine. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 &lsquo;ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn&rsquo; ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1eeda sai khi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Nga \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3&nbsp;HLV Vukojevic v\u00e0 Vida c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u xin l\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng khai. Tuy nhi\u00ean ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Croatia v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Vukojevjc b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf \u0110T Croatia ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup s\u1edbm. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nikola Kalinic c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 sau h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn Croatia g\u1eb7p Nigeria.&nbsp;H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Kalinic \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Zlatko Dalic n\u1ed5i gi\u1eadn&nbsp;v\u00e0 v\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u1eb3ng c\u1ed5 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 &lsquo;c\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u&rsquo; ra kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch&nbsp;World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7. \u1ede cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c2u s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/modric-la-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-190810.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/modric-la-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/modric-la-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-190810.html\">Modric l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nMandzukic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110T Croatia. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\">Mandzukic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mario Mandzukic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, HLV Croatia, Zlatko Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1088","checkdouble":"190822"},{"date":"08:35 10/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ngh\u0129 sao khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u201ck\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c\u201d Henry?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nguoi-phap-nghi-sao-khi-chuan-bi-doi-dau-ke-phan-quoc-henry.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 khi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 Brazil v\u00e0 Uruguay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 h\u1eb9n nhau m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Anh ho\u1eb7c Croatia.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0n anh ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c Henry h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0n anh ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c Henry h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/702451-lukaku-henry-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \"ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c\" Henry</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a Thierry Henry, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Roberto Martinez \u1edf\u2026 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9. Trong khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u201c\u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ea7n gi\u00f3\u201d ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m ngh\u0129, \u0111\u00e0n em Olivier Giroud \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u201ck\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c\u201d:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadt l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm khi Henry s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi cho Henry th\u1ea5y anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n sai b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn nh\u1ea7m n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. Th\u1ef1c l\u00f2ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i d\u0129 nhi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n Henry \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng sao c\u1ea3, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Giroud c\u00f3 l\u1ebd nh\u00e2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u00eau kh\u00edch Henry, khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n gi\u1eefa hai th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Arsenal n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Khi Giroud c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7, Henry cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0m trung phong.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00eam nay \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, Giroud h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 ra sao, Henry c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1087","checkdouble":"190824"},{"date":"08:42 10/07","title":"Sao Man Utd c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/18/sao-man-utd-co-tinh-choc-gian-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nemanja Matic c\u1ed1 \u00fd tr\u00e1i l\u1eddi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Serbia b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Khi \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Serbia n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f9a r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Nemanja Matic s\u1edbm tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man Utd \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao MU Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao MU Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/matic-da-co-keo-voi-man-utd-tu-khi-con-la-quan-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n khi Serbia b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 Brazil v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean Matic \u0111\u00fang th\u1eadt s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 b\u00ean \u00f4ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i vui v\u1ebb chia s\u1ebb anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u201cch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft ra sao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng? \u1eea th\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00e1i l\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed5i gi\u1eadn. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Serbia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 Mourinho lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u0103m nay, Man Utd s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean ICC, \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ba \u00f4ng l\u1edbn l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 AC Milan (25/7), Liverpool (28/7) v\u00e0 Real Madrid (31/7).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/131008-lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 - K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 International Champions Cup</span><br>\r\nBongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 International Champions Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi 18 CLB tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb 21/7 \u0111\u1ebfn 12/8</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1086","checkdouble":"190826"},{"date":"20:16 09/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi HLV Fernando Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luis Enrique - HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c khi &quot;La Roja&quot; \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Enrique tro thanh HLV truong DT Tay Ban Nha.\" title=\"Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi RFEF. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch RFEF Luis Rubiales cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Luis Enrique. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Francisco Molina - t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a RFEF cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, theo k\u1ecbp xu h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Luis Enrique t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft AS Roma, Celta Vigo v\u00e0 Barcelona. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf c\u00f9ng Barcelona, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2014-15.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Luis Enrique tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">La Roja h\u1ebft s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. RFEF sau \u0111\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro l\u00e0m HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hierro phat bieu sau tran TBN vs Nga\" title=\"Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Fernando Hierro t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Sau khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Fernando Hierro kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0o v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ch\u1ee9c v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, Fernando Hierro c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Francisco Molina Jimenez, m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1c ti\u1ebfp nhi\u1ec7m.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-thoi-ky-den-toi-da-quay-tro-lai-466-190370.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111en t\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro-421-190365.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 r\u1eddi World Cup, L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf HLV Hierro</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1085","checkdouble":"190800"},{"date":"20:50 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 9/7: \"Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/diem-tin-toi-97-kylian-mbappe-xung-gianh-qua-bong-vang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 9/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 10 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Daniel Fuzato (21 tu\u1ed5i) t\u1eeb Palmeiras v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 97 Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 97 Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-World-Cup-Cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-Pogbappe-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard cho r\u1eb1ng Kylian Mabppe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng cao qu\u00fd. Ch\u00ednh Mabppe g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 trao gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia, Fabien Delph cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau ph\u00fat n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 mong ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jordan Henderson c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Jamie Vardy c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">BTC ASIAD 2018 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0a hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eafng Sime Vrsaljko trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Anh. Vrsaljko d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nga \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Beckham l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Becks cho r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o m\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3ng 3.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua bia cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Slavonski Brod khi h\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Croatia.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190800.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/ever-banega-nut-thao-go-cho-messi-392-190799.html\">Ever Banega: N\u00fat th\u00e1o g\u